messageBody:
I am the moderator who allowed your message in. Due to previous
problems with spam, the owner of this list asked people to help with
allowing appropriate messages in. I suppose I was the only one not
busy at the time. We regret the delay in your message.

<jfcolson@b...> wrote:
> Hello everybody,
>
> Could someone explain why my message appeared only 11 h 18 min after
I've
> sent it?
>
> Meanwhile, I've read David Dailey's answer and downloaded the PDF file.
>
> JF
